              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "New cross sections for the 27Al(p,x)7Be nuclear",
                "process: Monitoring proton beam energy via the 22Na/7Be",
                "cross-section ratio between 45 and 200MeV"
